/>
to&nbsp;temporary switch application compile <br
/>mode to&nbsp;<b>SFU</b> (Single File Url mode).</li><li>
Visit all application routes where are different CSS or JS assets groups to complete
all possible asset files in <b><code>/Var/Tmp</code></b> directory. Process those requests
on addresses with the same or empty request base path as result application will have.</li><li>
Run <b><code>/make-php.php</code></b> script in browser or in CLI to build result application.
Do not include any PHP autoloaders, any unnecessary code you don't need and any source CSS/JS
